exhibition. Enjoy the flame war and keep posting nonsense - as usual
this will have the result to make the whole net.world dislike you and
oppose to any of your beliefs, just because you have adopted them.
Hopefully, this will make PGP and widespread use of public key
encryption even more popular - regardless of any patents, export
